的<rss version="2.0" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/"><channel><title>医学新闻</title><description>来自 News-Medical.Net - 来自世界各地的最新医学新闻和研究</description><link/>https://www.news-medical.net/<language>英文</language><item><title>所谓的“孤儿药”为制药公司赚的钱与主流药物一样多</title><description>据西弗吉尼亚大学的一位研究人员称，用于治疗罕见疾病的药物为制药公司带来的收入几乎与向公众销售的药物一样多。法学院教授肖恩·图 (Sean Tu) 发现利润丰厚的所谓“孤儿”药物可以获得制造税收抵免，专利独占期更长，并且更容易受到食品和药物管理局的审查。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/So-called-e2809corphane2809d-drugs-earn-pharmaceutical-companies-as-much-money-as-mainstream-medicines.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/So-called-e2809corphane2809d-drugs-earn-pharmaceutical-companies-as-much-money-as-mainstream-medicines.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=793dd197-6ede-43d2-8670-eaeec4e149f0</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 14:11:00 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2018/7/By_Gorodenkoff_571684e159074a84992c0edbe24d0030-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[So-called “orphan” drugs earn pharmaceutical companies as much money as mainstream medicines]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>研究表明邻里特征如何影响出生体重结果</title><description>哥伦比亚梅尔曼公共卫生学院的一项新研究表明，不健康零售食品店的社区密度越高，生下大于胎龄儿的风险越高，而健康食品零售店密度高的社区机构与生下小于胎龄儿的风险较低有关。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Study-shows-how-neighborhood-characteristics-may-affect-birthweight-outcomes.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Study-shows-how-neighborhood-characteristics-may-affect-birthweight-outcomes.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=abacc25f-8b1d-4150-88d8-1fc9d630a3b8</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 14:05:32 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/6/Pregnancy-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Study shows how neighborhood characteristics may affect birthweight outcomes]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>新的数据挑战旨在揭示脂蛋白 (a) 水平如何影响心血管疾病的风险</title><description>美国心脏协会是世界领先的专注于心脏和大脑健康的志愿组织，它邀请全球的科学研究人员参加一项新的数据挑战，以更好地科学理解脂蛋白 (a) [Lp(a)] 水平如何影响心血管疾病和中风的风险。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Researchers-Win-Up-To-2440K-Studying-Effects-Of-Lipoprotein(A)-On-Cardiovascular-Disease-Stroke-Risk.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Researchers-Win-Up-To-2440K-Studying-Effects-Of-Lipoprotein(A)-On-Cardiovascular-Disease-Stroke-Risk.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=376ff84d-58ba-4b86-90d5-a5b76d3a6556</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 13:59:00 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/9/heart_disease_1_12c3ff20f43b43d898bf18f5689e0c7c-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[New data challenge seeks to unravel how lipoprotein(a) levels impact risk of cardiovascular disease]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>人工智能技术在分析冠状动脉造影方面显示出巨大潜力</title><description>发表在 JMIR Cardio 上的新研究揭示了人工智能 (AI) 技术在分析冠状动脉造影术（冠状动脉疾病的常见诊断程序）方面的巨大潜力。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/AI-technology-shows-remarkable-potential-in-analyzing-coronary-angiography.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/AI-technology-shows-remarkable-potential-in-analyzing-coronary-angiography.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=163afb76-7938-47c7-ad3d-3ca91a36f876</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 13:53:24 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2019/5/futuristic_techno_design_on_background_of_supercomputer_data_center_-_Image_-_Timofeev_Vladimir_M1_402c068791b640469e416c4f55d84afe-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[AI technology shows remarkable potential in analyzing coronary angiography]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>肥胖相关的癌症风险因生理性别而异</title><description>许多研究已将肥胖与癌症风险增加联系起来，但大多数研究并未区分男性和女性之间的风险。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Adiposity-associated-cancer-risk-differs-based-on-biological-sex.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Adiposity-associated-cancer-risk-differs-based-on-biological-sex.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=7ca19fa4-6c5f-4f8b-9e4f-f4298d4d203a</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 13:45:20 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2017/3/Obesity-Jakub_Cejpek_ead0fb8492f0437f96e9fd842630990c-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Adiposity-associated cancer risk differs based on biological sex]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>科学家找到了我们如何在饭后保持恒定血糖水平的线索</title><description>柏林夏里特健康研究所 (BIH) 的科学家和英国同事发现了关于我们如何在进食后保持恒定血糖水平的线索。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Scientists-find-clues-to-how-we-maintain-constant-blood-sugar-levels-after-meals.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Scientists-find-clues-to-how-we-maintain-constant-blood-sugar-levels-after-meals.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=08217bc9-5732-4016-9095-7f90ae722c6e</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 13:39:59 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2017/1/image_(6)_1b78fec41a5143afb6e7b9ad317023d2-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Scientists find clues to how we maintain constant blood sugar levels after meals]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>研究为对 CAR T 细胞疗法反应不完全的血癌患者带来了新希望</title><description>免疫治疗策略的目的是利用患者自身免疫系统中的细胞来破坏肿瘤细胞。 CAR T细胞疗法是一种免疫疗法，可有效治疗血癌。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Study-raises-new-hopes-for-blood-cancer-patients-with-an-incomplete-response-to-CAR-T-cell-therapy。 ASPX<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Study-raises-new-hopes-for-blood-cancer-patients-with-an-incomplete-response-to-CAR-T-cell-therapy。 aspx#评论</comments><guid>https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=d954228a-389e-4802-8a2f-bac7b486b0a2</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 13:34:22 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2016/3/Cancer_blood_5431357749be4138a37404d0991ed04a-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Study raises new hopes for blood cancer patients with an incomplete response to CAR T cell therapy]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>研究人员发现糖分子如何影响癌细胞对放化疗的反应</title><description>乔治敦大学隆巴尔迪综合癌症中心的研究人员及其同事一直在探索与癌症发展有关的生化途径的复杂性，他们发现一种形式的葡萄糖（一种糖）与用于构建 DNA 分子的途径错综复杂地相关联。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Researchers-discover-how-a-sugar-molecule-can-affect-cancer-cell-response-to-chemoradiotherapy.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Researchers-discover-how-a-sugar-molecule-can-affect-cancer-cell-response-to-chemoradiotherapy.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=ce2f281c-e4e3-42d4-8362-0b39379680c7</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 13:25:03 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/7/174318220-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Researchers discover how a sugar molecule can affect cancer cell response to chemoradiotherapy]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>新材料有望引领下一代癌症治疗</title><description>一种在有机化学和无机化学鲜为人知的交叉点上创造的新材料，不仅可以实现更强大的太阳能电池板，而且还可以引领下一代癌症治疗。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/New-material-could-usher-in-the-next-generation-of-cancer-treatments.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/New-material-could-usher-in-the-next-generation-of-cancer-treatments.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=729be2ff-7a56-494e-a711-484711cf0fb7</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 13:17:37 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/7/cancer_cell-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[New material could usher in the next generation of cancer treatments]]></media:description></media:content></item><item><title>研究为多发性骨髓瘤的演变提供了新的见解</title><description>德克萨斯大学 MD 安德森癌症中心的研究人员进行的一项新研究强调了多发性骨髓瘤从前体疾病演变而来的新见解，这可能有助于更好地识别可能进展的患者并制定新的干预措施。</description><link/> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Study-offers-novel-insights-into-the-evolution-of-multiple-myeloma.aspx<comments> https://www.news-medical.net/news/20230612/Study-offers-novel-insights-into-the-evolution-of-multiple-myeloma.aspx#comment</comments><guid> https://www.news-medical.net/post.aspx?id=1237a514-daf3-49a4-acde-0adc61344085</guid><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 13:12:45 -0400</pubDate> <media:content expression="full" height="480" type="image/jpeg" url="https://d2jx2rerrg6sh3.cloudfront.net/image-handler/picture/2014/7/DNA_Genetics-620x480.jpg" width="620"><media:description><![CDATA[Study offers novel insights into the evolution of multiple myeloma]]></media:description></media:content></item></channel></rss>